quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  42,1,"Haa, Miim"
  42,2,"Ain, Siin, Qaaf"
  42,3,"Ko wano nii woni ko Allah Teɗɗuɗo, Ñeeño On wahayiniri e maa, e ɓen adinooɓe ma"
  42,4,"Ko Kanko woodani kala ko woni ka kammuuli e ka leydi. Ko Kanko kadi woni Toowuɗo, Mawɗo On"
  42,5,"Kammuuli ɗin no eɓɓa seekorgol dow majji, hara Malaa'ika'en no subbunhinanora yettugol Joomi maɓɓe, ɓe insinanoo wonɓe ka leydi ɓen. Anndee pellet, ko Allah woni Haforoowo, Hinnotooɗo On"
  42,6,"Ɓen non jogitiiɓe yiɗɓe goo gaanin Makko, Allah ko reenuɗo ɓe. A wonaali reenoowo ɓe"
  42,7,"Ko wano non Men wahayniri e maaɗa, janngeteende e aarabu, fii yo a jertin yimɓe neene ca'e ɗen e wonɓe takko mayre ɓen, jertinaa fii ñalnde dental nden, - nde sikke alaa e mu'un - Fedde goo ka Aljnna, fedde goo kadi ka Yiite"
  42,8,"Si Allah haajuno, O waɗayno ɓe mofte goote. Kono himo On mo O muuyi ka Yurmeende Makko. Tooñooɓe ɓen non, giɗo alanaa ɓe, wanaa ballo"
  42,9,"Kaa ɓe jogiti yiɗɓe goo gaanin Makko? Awa ko Allah woni Giɗo On, ko Kanko wuurnitata maayɓe ɓen; ko Kanko kadi woni kaɗtanɗo kala huunde"
  42,10,"Kala ko luutondirɗon e fii mun, haray ñaawoore mun nden ko ka Allah woni. Ko On mooɗon Allah, woni Joomi am; ko e Makko mi fawii, ko ka Makko kadi mi ruttorta [tuubugol]"